OL,3,COmagh bomb families call for special
OL,4,Cadvocate for closed hearings at inquiry
OL,6,FSurvivors and families of those killed
OL,7,Fin the Omagh bomb have asked to be
OL,8,Frepresented by a special advocate in
OL,9,Fclosed hearings at the public inquiry.
OL,11,FOmagh Bombing Inquiry chairman Lord
OL,12,FTurnbull is hearing arguments around
OL,13,Fapplications during dedicated hearings
OL,14,Fthis week.
OL,16,FCounsel to the inquiry Paul Greaney KC
OL,17,Fsaid the inquiry, which is probing
OL,18,Fwhether the 1998 dissident republican
OL,19,Fbomb attack could have been prevented,
OL,20,Fwill hear some sensitive security
OL,21,Fevidence in closed hearings.
