OL,3,COmagh bomb families call for special
OL,4,Cadvocate for closed hearings at inquiry
OL,6,FThe atrocity in the Co Tyrone town on
OL,7,FAugust 15 1998 killed 29 people,
OL,8,Fincluding a woman pregnant with twins.
OL,10,FSpeaking during hearings in Belfast on
OL,11,FMonday, Mr Greaney said the inquiry's
OL,12,Flegal team recognises that survivors
OL,13,Fand the bereaved have spent 25 seeking
OL,14,Fthe truth, and may be "suspicious or
OL,15,Feven cynical of the UK state's
OL,16,Fwillingness to engage in a way that is
OL,17,Fstraightforward and wholehearted with
OL,18,Fthis inquiry".
